4 DEMONSTRATION
We implemented the Privata framework as a web application. In this section, we describe the registration and the response of questions, negotiation and the transaction in the Privata framework with the screenshot. The Privata consumer and provider register their email and password first. The consumer generates a question that he/she wants to collect the data with the minimum Îµ value, the desired price, the required number of provider, and the available budget for the negotiation. There are two types of data types that can be selected: categorical and numeric.

